Upstream lineage
----------------
Maestro Spine adapts operating patterns from Garry Tan's MIT-licensed gstack
(https://github.com/garrytan/gstack) and gbrain (https://github.com/garrytan/gbrain).
Their MIT license texts are preserved in THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md, and the specific
patterns adapted are documented in ACKNOWLEDGMENTS.md.

